quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Taa seen Meem
  26,2,Yeh kitaab e Mubeen ki aayat hain
  26,3,"(Aey Muhammad), shayad tum is gham (grief) mein apni jaan kho dogey ke yeh log iman nahin latey"
  26,4,Hum chahein to aasmaan se aisi nishani nazil kar sakte hain ke inki gardanein iske aagey jhuk jayein
  26,5,In logon ke paas rehman ki taraf se jo nayi naseehat bhi aati hai yeh ussey mooh moad letey hain
  26,6,"Ab ke yeh jhutla chuke hain, ankareeb inko is cheez ki haqeeqat (mukhtalif tareeqon se) maloom ho jayegi jiska yeh mazaak udatay rahey hain"
  26,7,Aur kya inhon ne kabhi zameen par nigaah nahin daali ke humne kitni kaseer miqdaar mein har tarah ki umdah nabataat(vegetation) ismein paida ki hain
  26,8,"Yaqeenen ismein ek nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar maanne waley nahin"
  26,9,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,10,Inhein us waqt ka qissa sunao jabke tumhare Rubb ne Moosa ko pukara “ zaalim qaum ke paas jaa
  26,11,"Firoun ki qaum ke paas, kya woh nahin darte?”"
  26,12,"Usne arz kiya “aey Rubb, mujhey khauf hai ke woh mujhey jhutla dengey"
  26,13,"Mera seena ghutt-ta hai aur meri zubaan nahin chalti, aap Haroon ki taraf risalat bhejein"
  26,14,"Aur mujhpar unke haan ek jurm ka ilzam bhi hai, is liye main darta hoon ke woh mujhey qatal kar dengey”"
  26,15,"Farmaya “hargiz nahin, tum dono jao hamari nishaniyan lekar, hum tumhare saath sab kuch suntey rahenge"
  26,16,"Firoun ke paas jao aur ussey kaho, humko Rubb ul aalameen ne isliye bheja hai"
  26,17,Ke tu bani Israel ko hamare saath janey de”
  26,18,Firoun ne kaha “kya humne tujhko apne haan baccha sa nahin paala tha? Tu nay apni umar ke kai saal hamare haan guzare
  26,19,"Aur iske baad kar gaya jo kuch ke kar gaya, tu bada ehsan faramosh aadmi hai”"
  26,20,Moosa ne jawab diya “us waqt woh kaam maine nadanishtagi (inadvertently) mein kardiya tha
  26,21,Phir main tumhare khauf se bhaag gaya. Iske baad mere Rubb ne mujhko hukum ata kiya aur mujhey Rasoolon mein shamil farma liya
  26,22,Raha tera ehsan jo tu nay mujhpar jataya hai to iski haqeeqat yeh hai ke tu nay bani Israel ko ghulaam bana liya tha”
  26,23,Firoun ne kaha “aur yeh Rubb-ul-Aalameen kya hota hai?”
  26,24,"Moosa ne jawab diya “Aasmano aur zameen ka Rubb, aur un sab cheezon ka Rubb jo aasmaan o zameen ke darmiyan hain, agar tum yaqeen laney waley ho.”"
  26,25,Firoun ne apne gird o pesh ke logon se kaha ‘Sunte ho?”
  26,26,"Moosa ne kaha, “tumhara Rubb bhi aur tumhare un aabaa o ajdaad ka Rubb bhi jo guzar chuke hain”"
  26,27,"Firoun ne ( haazirin se) kaha “ tumhare yeh Rasool sahib jo tumhari taraf bhejey gaye hain, bilkul hi pagal maloom hotay hain”"
  26,28,"Moosa ne kaha “mashriq o magrib aur jo kuch inke darmiyan hai sabka Rubb, agar aap log kuch aqal rakhte hain”"
  26,29,Firoun ne kaha “ agar tu nay mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood maana to tujhey main un logon mein shamil kardunga jo qaid khano mein paday saddh(rotting) rahey hain”
  26,30,Moosa ne kaha “Agarche main le aaon tere saamne ek sareeh cheez bhi?”
  26,31,Firoun ne kaha “Accha to le aa agar tu saccha hai”
  26,32,(Uski zubaan se yeh baat nikalte hi) Moosa ne apna asa (staff) phenka aur yakayak woh ek sareeh azdha (serpant/snake) tha
  26,33,Phir usne apna hath (bagal se) khincha aur wo sab dekne walon ke saamne chamak raha tha
  26,34,Firoun apne gird o pesh ke sardaron se bola “yeh shaks yaqeenan ek maahir jaadugar hai
  26,35,"Chahta hai ke apne jaadu ke zoar se tumko tumhare mulk se nikal de, ab tum batao tum kya hukum dete ho?”"
  26,36,Unhon ne kaha “ isey aur iske bhai ko rok lijiye aur shehron mein harkare (heralds) bhej dijiye
  26,37,Ke har siyane jaadugar ko aapke paas le aayein”
  26,38,Chunanchey ek roz muqarrar waqt par jaadugar ikatthey karliye gaye
  26,39,Aur logon se kaha gaya “tum ijtima mein chaloge
  26,40,Shayad ke hum jaadugaron ke deen hi par reh jayein agar woh gaalib rahey”
  26,41,Jab jaadugar maidan mein aa gaye to unhon ne Firoun se kaha “humein inaam to milega agar hum gaalib rahey?”
  26,42,"Usne kaha “ haan, aur tum to us waqt muqarrabeen (nearest to me) mein shamil ho jaogey”"
  26,43,Moosa ne kaha “ phenko jo tumhein phenkna hai”
  26,44,Unhon ne fawran apni rassiyan aur laathiyan phenk di aur bole “ Firoun ke iqbal se hum hi gaalib rahenge.”
  26,45,Phir Moosa ne apna asa (staff) phenka to yakayak woh unke jhootey karishmon ko hadap karta chala ja raha tha
  26,46,Ispar sarey jaadugar be-ikhtiyar sajde mein gir paday
  26,47,Aur bol uthey ke “ maan gaye hum Rubb-ul-Aalameen ko
  26,48,Moosa aur Haroon ke Rubb ko”
  26,49,"Firoun ne kaha “tum Moosa ki baat maan gaye qabl iske ke main tumhein ijazat deta! Zaroor yeh tumhara bada hai jisne tumhein jaadu sikhaya hai. Accha, abhi tumhein maloom hua jaata hai, main tumhare haath paon mukhalif simton (opposite sides) mein katwaunga aur tum sabko sooli (crucify) chadha dunga”"
  26,50,"Unhon ne jawab diya “kuch parwah nahin, hum apne Rubb ke huzur pahunch jayenge"
  26,51,Aur humein tawaqqu hai ke hamara Rubb hamare gunaah maaf kardega kyunke sabse pehle hum iman laye hain”